Aleman traveled Wednesday to San Jose, Costa Rica, to participate
in Brazilian and Central American presidential summit.
</P>
<P>
Among the issues covered during this meeting are the
strengthening of democracy, human development, overcoming poverty,
environmental protection.
</P>
