the March 26 balloting by collecting 52.94 percent of the votes.
</P>
<P>
The official result will be published in the newspapers
Rossiiskaya Gazeta and Parlamentskaya Gazeta Friday.
</P>
<P>
Putin is expected to be sworn into office in 30 days. (Russia-
Putin-President) 
