Hornets, Alonzo Mourning of the Miami Heats, Ray Allen of the
Milwaukee Bucks, Keith Van Horn of the New Jersey Nets, Darrell
Armstrong of the Orlando Magics, Clifford Robinson of the Phoenix
Suns, Vince Carter of the Toronto Raptors and Gary Payton of the
Seattle Supersonics.
</P>
<P>
Steve Francis of the Houston Rockets won the award of the
Rookie of the Month for March and Jerry Sloan of the Utah Jazz was
named the Coach of the Month. 
