research and development of gene study on Chinese people, Shanghai
Genecore Biotechnologies Ltd was jointly set up by three American
companies in 1997, including PE Biosystems and Celera Genomics
Company.
</P>
<P>
Over the past two years, the enterprise has engaged in a series
of key cooperation projects with Chinese research institutes on
the mensuration of genes of liver cancer and viruses, among others.
</P>
<P>
