<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, April 5 (Xinhua) -- Thailand is now well-prepared for
hosting the Asian Development Bank (ADB) meeting, to be held in
the northern resort province of Chiang Mai next month, the Thai
News Agency (TNA) reported Wednesday.
</P>
