officers had learned from the 10th Session of the United Nations
Conference on Trade and Development (UNCTAD X), which was held in
Bangkok in February, he said.
</P>
<P>
Thai security officers are, therefore, ready for the upcoming
ADB conference, he noted.
</P>
<P>
In other areas, authorities concerned are also reportedly ready
for the meeting of the Manila-based financial institute, which is
a major support for development projects of developing countries
in the region. 
